    {
      "id": "p2-tools",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 790,
      "y": 575,
      "width": 400,
      "height": 160,
      "text": "New tools per archetype:\n  CODE_BUILD: + hadolint, yamllint, docker-compose-config\n  SYSTEM_DESIGN: + check_design_structure\n  AI_PROMPT: + validate_csv, check_data_patterns\n  NON_TECH: + validate_csv, time_estimate\n\nNew infra:\n  + DeepEval (structured evals, replaces evals.py)\n  + SemHash (deduplication)\n  + Chroma (knowledge retrieval)\n  + Context7 MCP (live library docs)",
