    {
      "id": "p3-new",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 810,
      "y": 845,
      "width": 380,
      "height": 180,
      "text": "New capabilities:\n  + Two-phase generators (PR_REVIEW, CODE_DEBUG)\n  + Solver Agent (empirical difficulty calibration)\n  + E2B/Daytona sandboxed code execution\n  + SWE-bench fail-to-pass verification\n  + Testcontainers (Postgres/Kafka/Redis)\n  + DSPy + MIPROv2 prompt optimization\n\nArchitecture:\n  Coordinator = OpenAI's \"Manager Pattern\"\n  Generators = Workers (one per task, parallel)\n  Eval = Evaluator-Optimizer loop (per worker)",
      "fontSize": 11,
      "fontFamily": 3,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "strokeColor": "#5c5f66",
      "backgroundColor": "transparent",
      "fillStyle": "solid",
      "strokeWidth": 1,
      "roughness": 1,
      "opacity": 100,
      "angle": 0,
      "seed": 870,
